metadata.name: Galactic #1
metadata.description:
Robot BH2.0 Titanium Blue of the Galactic Federation of Arturians

Rank : 3 / Main quality: Selflessness. Robot with artificial intelligence, very friendly and has no aggressive skills, though he looks almost like a fighter. Can stand up for himself and protect his comrade. Irreplaceable assistant in everyday life. Very appreciated among the Arturians, proved himself as a robot with soul, loyalty is his most important quality. Many cases with this model of robot, when he saved lives by sacrificing himself. There are additional materials.
